to thief city,terrorist city,center
city,pirate bay,or King Slug's Castle.
You should go to central city and learn
more information.
@match king|Slug|King Slug
King Slug is our ruler. His domain is
under Yoer city and his domain is
called the Criminal Underworld of Yoer.
We are getting more powerful! Soon we
will overthrow the king's son and rule
Yoer city! We will build an empire!!!

endmsg
